{"tid":2272873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國公佈海警法草案允許對外國船隻開火 尖閣諸島衝突可能加劇","createTime":"2020-11-05T10:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T11:35:47.000Z","uid":75656,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed019f66a86efd5bbdda6cb464b20b086fcce48","tid":2272873,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"中國昨天（4日）公佈海警法草案全文，<span class=\"red\">允許中國海警在警告無效或情況緊急時，得以使用攜帶的武器</span>，對此，日方認為，因中國主張擁有釣魚台列嶼（日本稱尖閣諸島）主權，<span class=\"red\">未來日本漁船及保安廳船隻在該區恐成中國海警局對付的對象</span>。<br />\n<br />\n據《共同社》代表，中國全國人民代表大會昨天（4日）公佈海警法草案全文，內容允許中國海警局使用武器，稱「外國船隻在中國管轄海域進行違法活動、不遵從海警局停船命令等情況下允許使用武器」，而中國主張擁有釣魚台列嶼主權。<br />\n<br />\n《共同社》指出，中國海警法草案除針對釣魚台列嶼外，亦考量到南海局勢，還列了保衛人工島礁得採取的必要措施，日媒提及，如此一來，在釣魚台列嶼附近行駛的日本漁船恐成為對象，另外在該地區與中方對峙的日本海上保安廳也有可能對象。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，中國海警法草案規定，當警告無效或情況緊急時，中方「可以使用攜帶的武器」，並指明，除了應付海上恐怖活動及重大武力事件外，若受到攻擊，中國也可以動用海警局船隻及航空器所配備的武器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3342695\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3342695&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4En12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=dcf3e243\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3342695&h=2f900cfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3342695</a>"},{"pid":"38a8a7c53352c34de64c250f5f562848f6a4249e","tid":2272873,"uid":33370,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"日本：解。除。封。印。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYJfRaP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYJfRaP.gif&h=7be7daf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e73ba8dead2b321502f77ba61f8c15c4a10e21ad","tid":2272873,"uid":16057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38a8a7c53352c34de64c250f5f562848f6a4249e","tid":2272873,"uid":33370,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"日本：解。除。封。印。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYJfRaP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYJfRaP.gif&h=7be7daf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"拜登唔比"},{"pid":"2e3f4bc75c7adac366491122bf2b6659b36c6309","tid":2272873,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"問咗拜登未？<br />\n要日本嘔返釣魚台出黎"},{"pid":"245a012b3b8fd6528b77ba17fc19360ae794091e","tid":2272873,"uid":35430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:09:41.000Z","msg":"一知道拜登贏面大就即刻得寸進尺"},{"pid":"0b71d94a586364541fd5e7a3228dd582cb5eee28","tid":2272873,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"射一炮就斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a09867bd77374c149e457377c30e5333d70909","tid":2272873,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"日本要靠自己啦"},{"pid":"91b015c9fd37b8c1434a3baecf4ea9a934a33928","tid":2272873,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:14:03.000Z","msg":"打啦！最好打到珍珠港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00255ab0e310693c33b9b7661e328ff3c13b1c9","tid":2272873,"uid":47259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:19:30.000Z","msg":"支那勁多漁船軍用<br />\n即係普通漁船都大條道理射鳩你"},{"pid":"67cf6ede5582dabe54b655e3f68e0a1c9272bdb1","tid":2272873,"uid":34065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"最撚怕你唔射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cd41d3f0be482342964818c8a2d79a6396cbc1","tid":2272873,"uid":323720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91b015c9fd37b8c1434a3baecf4ea9a934a33928","tid":2272873,"